  "detailed_description": "<h1>FIND HMUR!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563830/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.poster.avif?t=1764410114\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563830/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.webm?t=1764410114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563830/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.mp4?t=1764410114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563830/extras/ec6a2575034de49a4ceb0bf6b117e56a.avif?t=1764410114\" width=610 height=189 /></span><br><br>Battle Cat vs Treacherous Mice - a game in which you shoot dangerous creatures on the surface under the control of treacherous mice. Mice sit underground and cause a lot of trouble. Your task is to complete all the levels and clear the surface of pests.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563830/extras/5549f97d112013ee9b3e74cd358abef1.poster.avif?t=1764410114\" width=594 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563830/extras/5549f97d112013ee9b3e74cd358abef1.webm?t=1764410114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563830/extras/5549f97d112013ee9b3e74cd358abef1.mp4?t=1764410114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Features of the game:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Endless rounds of ammo!<br></li><li>Treacherous mice!<br></li><li>Achievements for completing levels!<br></li><li>Teleports!<br></li><li>Doors!<br></li><li>Milk - YES, milk is a first-aid kit!<br></li><li>Jumping off the walls!<br></li><li>Complex mechanisms with saws!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563830/extras/0c573d9a89ab527ab53c4b3c6543b2f8.poster.avif?t=1764410114\" width=594 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563830/extras/0c573d9a89ab527ab53c4b3c6543b2f8.webm?t=1764410114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563830/extras/0c573d9a89ab527ab53c4b3c6543b2f8.mp4?t=1764410114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
